quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  12,43,"Umwami (yaje kurota), aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri narose mbona inka ndwi zishishe ziribwa n’inka ndwi z’imiguta, (mbona) n’amahundo arindwi mabisi n’andi (arindwi) yumye. Yemwe byegera byanjye! Nimunsobanurire inzozi zanjye, niba koko muzi gusobanura inzozi.”"
  12,44,"Baravuga bati “(Izo nzozi zawe) ni uruvangitirane, ntizisobanutse, kandi ntabwo turi abahanga bo gusobanura inzozi (nk’izo).”"
  12,45,"Maze wa muntu warekuwe (mu bari bafunganywe na Yusufu) aza kwibuka nyuma y’igihe (ko atamuvuganiye), maze aravuga ati “Njye ndababwira ibisobanuro byazo, ngaho nimunyohereze (kuri Yusufu).”"
  12,46,"(Aravuga ati) “Yewe Yusufu w’umunyakuri! Dusobanurire iby’inka ndwi zishishe ziribwa n’izindi indwi z’imiguta, n’iby’amahundo arindwi mabisi n’andi (arindwi) yumye, kugira ngo nsubire ku bantu (bantumye), bityo basobanukirwe (iby’izo nzozi).”"
  12,47,"(Yusufu) aravuga ati “Muzahinga imyaka irindwi ikurikirana, maze ibyo muzasarura muzabirekere mu misogwe yabyo, usibye bike mu byo muzarya.”"
  12,48,"“Nyuma y’icyo gihe, hazaza (imyaka) irindwi (y’amapfa) izarya ibyo muzaba mwarayihunikiye, usibye bike muzaba mwarazigamye (nk’imbuto).”"
  12,49,“Maze nyuma yayo haze umwaka abantu babone imvura nyinshi (beze byinshi) nuko benge (imitobe myinshi).”